{"tid":1210182,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"細細時會整啲丫叉彈雀","createTime":"2019-06-12T13:14:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-13T21:55:26.000Z","uid":242980,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"02139fb4f1b6f3af90aa8e881bbb036666ecc555","tid":1210182,"uid":242980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T13:14:11.000Z","msg":"可惜一隻都彈唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n危險嘢嚟，有機會彈傷人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n千祈唔好亂咁玩！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2uUEr7y.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2uUEr7y.png&h=cd7419fc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ddb9f68c3be05448dc2129825c718f83f110bf81","tid":1210182,"uid":256688,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T21:27:27.000Z","msg":"彈弓[編輯]<br />\n<br />\n維基百科，自由的百科全書<br />\n<br />\n跳至導覽跳至搜尋<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;本文介紹的是一種小型投石器。關於機械零件，請見「彈簧」。<br />\n<br />\n張仙使用彈弓（Pebble bow）向天狗射擊。<br />\n<br />\n彈弓可作為冷兵器或玩具。傳統的彈弓（Pebble bow）外形和普通的弓一樣，但是使用雙弦，用泥陶做彈丸，主要用來活捉鳥雀。中國傳說中的祿神送子張仙就是使用彈弓的好手。[1]歐洲的達文西亦曾建議用彈弓來發射臭氣彈。元清武器管制較嚴，民間不許有弓，彈弓在民間流行，所以明末清初的武俠小說，很多大俠是使用彈弓泥丸的，明代因循古代射禮，並規定官學儒生必須習弓，不禁弓和冷兵器，彈弓則是小孩子遊戲。<br />\n<br />\nY字彈弓，使用彈性體長條來發射彈丸。<br />\n<br />\n另一種Y字彈弓（Slingshot）已知出現於硫化天然橡膠被發明的1839年之後。一般用樹枝、金屬或塑膠等材料製作Y形彈弓柄，Y形柄上兩頭系上彈性體長條，彈性體中段系上用來包裹彈丸的皮塊。Y字彈弓的威力取決於彈性體的拉力。彈性體拉力越大，彈弓的威力也越大。<br />\n<br />\n參考文獻[編輯]<br />\n<br />\n^&nbsp;《歲節的故事》，第227頁。殷登國 著。<br />\n<br />\n收立容易<br />\n進可攻<br />\n退可守<br />\n有遠程控制局面<br />\n唔駛埋牙戰<br />\n打游擊亦可<br />\n上彈街頭石仔無限供應<br />\n真係唔錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f32fcc0d37d8ffa280e6392043c1052cf120a76b","tid":1210182,"uid":209620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T21:28:37.000Z","msg":"屌 呢個真係又要推"},{"pid":"6233127be0ee805bcfea4383f3b3f0c0da7c3df3","tid":1210182,"uid":256688,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"f32fcc0d37d8ffa280e6392043c1052cf120a76b","tid":1210182,"uid":209620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T21:28:37.000Z","msg":"屌 呢個真係又要推"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T21:30:02.000Z","msg":"10 個人有10飛同時射<br />\n100 個有100 飛<br />\n1000 個有1000 飛etc....<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d39cb9bb80c3f12d559cd9a2ef617beb8e7e6dc4","tid":1210182,"uid":209620,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T21:31:32.000Z","msg":"係米討論緊新戲 讓丫叉飛"},{"pid":"04ef1e1bcab3a261ecff3556f0280fd3ed790200","tid":1210182,"uid":209620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T21:33:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e476fb8fd2a8c9e5e2e769e399b06bc54f0b4057","tid":1210182,"uid":209620,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T21:33:18.000Z","msg":"好耐無玩過 兒時回憶"},{"pid":"8d83b6b75dfead5949e3a5de924a944c0c773c31","tid":1210182,"uid":256688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d39cb9bb80c3f12d559cd9a2ef617beb8e7e6dc4","tid":1210182,"uid":209620,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T21:31:32.000Z","msg":"係米討論緊新戲 讓丫叉飛"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T21:34:00.000Z","msg":"係呀,youtube有預告,睇預告好似幾好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2da6a52c60549e8b25b053eab0a95a379e5ab4c1","tid":1210182,"uid":17832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T21:35:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"04674becbfc04595793fa54757a17edfa5163a4f","tid":1210182,"uid":256688,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"2da6a52c60549e8b25b053eab0a95a379e5ab4c1","tid":1210182,"uid":17832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T21:35:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T21:37:02.000Z","msg":"聽聞依家防野狗山狗幾work<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class